column5: Has anyone renewed their fishing license online - with success.  I had done it previously 3 years ago. Printed off temp license and received card in the mail.  Tried to renew online today and input all the info. In the license selection no license came up as an option.  Am I missing something or is their something up with the site?  Any input appreciated.  Nemo
I think I had problems but switching to Internet Explorer solved it.
Thanks Dennis switched to IE and all is good.  Nemo
